Package: tidyhelpr
Title: Helper functions for data wrangling with the tidyverse
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Butz", , "alexander.butz@statworx.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The tidyhelpr package is a conglomeration of useful helper function for data wrangling with the tidyverse. 
    It is (and per se will always be) work in progress as a function is added if roughly the same helper function is 
    used in multiple (non-related) projects and the function is nontrivial.
